dev-6.x.name: drupal/ajax_quiz

security-coverage.message: Dev releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

dev-6.x.description: This module doesn't degrade gracefully, and we don't recommend using it until it does. This module attempts to provide an AJAX version of quiz. Successive quiz questions will be loaded in the same page without page reload, but it doesn't work flawlessly at the moment.
